&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tip&lt;/strong&gt;: Replace the line above marked as &quot;Key Part&quot; with one of these lines, if you want to center the text:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Only vertically:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;lang-css s-code-block&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;hljs language-css&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-attribute&quot;&gt;margin&lt;/span&gt;: auto &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-number&quot;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Only horizontally:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;lang-css s-code-block&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;hljs language-css&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-attribute&quot;&gt;margin&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-number&quot;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; auto;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As I noticed, this trick works with grids (i.e. &lt;code&gt;display: grid&lt;/code&gt;), also.&lt;/p&gt;

